Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Description=Gets parameter values from a string.
Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Example.Description=Result \= StringFunctionsClientServer.ParametersFromString("File\=""c\:\\InfoBases\\Trade""; Usr\=""Director"";""", ";");\n- returns a structure\:\nkey "File" and value "c\:\\InfoBases\\Trade"\nkey "Usr"  and value "Director".
Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Name=ParametersFromString
Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Param.Разделитель.Description=character separating fragments from each other.
Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Param.Разделитель.Name=Separator
Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Param.СтрокаПараметров.Description=string containing parameters, each of which is\na fragment of the form <ParameterName>\=<Value>, where\nParameterName - parameter name;\nValue - its value.\nFragments are separated from each other by ';' characters.\nIf the value contains whitespace characters, it must be enclosed in double\nquotes (").\nFor example\:\n"File\=""c\:\\InfoBases\\Trade""; Usr\=""Director"";"
Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Param.СтрокаПараметров.Name=ParametersString
Method.ПараметрыИзСтроки.Return.Description=parameter values, where key - parameter name, value - parameter value.
