Method.ПодставитьПараметрыВСтроку.Description=Substitutes parameters into a string. Maximum number of parameters - 9.\nParameters in the string are specified as %<parameter number>. Parameter numbering starts from one.
Method.ПодставитьПараметрыВСтроку.Example.Description=StringFunctionsClientServer.SubstituteParametersInString(NStr("en\='%1 went to %2'"), "John", "Zoo") \= "John went\nto Zoo".
