Method.СтрокаСЧисломДляЛюбогоЯзыка.Description=Forms a number presentation for a specific language and number parameters.
Method.СтрокаСЧисломДляЛюбогоЯзыка.Example.Description=Parameter presentation\:\n\nLang | Zero | One             | Two            | Few               | Many                  | Other\n\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\nru   |      | XX1 / X11       |                | XX2-XX4 / X12-X14 | XX0, XX5-XX9, X11-X14 | fractional\nCard.|      | %1 day left     |                | %1 days left      | %1 days left          | %1 days left\n|      | I see %1 fish   |                | I see %1 fishes   | I see %5 fishes       | I see %1 fishes\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nru   |      |                 |                |                   |                       | none other\nOrd. |      |                 |                |                   |                       | day %1\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nen   |      | for 1           |                |                   |                       | other\nCard.|      | left %1 day     |                |                   |                       | left %1 days\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nen   |      | XX1 / X11       | XX2 / X12      | XX3 / X13         |                       | other\nOrd. |      | %1st day        | %1nd day       | %1rd day          |                       | %1th day.\nCard. - Cardinal;\nOrd.  - Ordinal;\nX - any digit;\n- except.\nString \= StringFunctionsClientServer.StringWithNumberForAnyLanguage(\nNStr("ru\=';остался %1 день;;осталось %1 дня;осталось %1 дней;осталось %1 дня';\n|en\=';left %1 day;;;;left %1 days'"),\n0.05,, "NFD\=1");
Method.СтрокаСЧисломДляЛюбогоЯзыка.Name=StringWithNumberForAnyLanguage
Method.СтрокаСЧисломДляЛюбогоЯзыка.Param.Вид.Name=Kind
Method.СтрокаСЧисломДляЛюбогоЯзыка.Param.Вид.Type.0.Description=Determines the kind of numeric value for which the presentation is formed.
